<b>Serious injury: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">Any condition that severely damaged the skin and its underlying tissue increases the risk of Gangrene.</span>

<b>Smoking: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">Those who smoke have a higher risk of developing Gangrene.</span>

